 mouse thread      |                           |
   calls new() --->|  Window struct             |
                   |    .id = 2                |
                   |    .pid -------+          |
                   |    .name = "window.2"     |
                   |    .img ------+|          |
                   |    .mch       ||          |
                   |               ||          |
                   |  window       ||          |
                   |  thread  <----+|          |
                   +-----------+---||----------+
                               |   ||
              draw (kernel)    |   ||   new process
           +-------------------+   ||  +----------+
           |   layer           |   |+->| /bin/rc  |
           |  "window.2"      |   |   +----+-----+
           |  (on desktop)     |   |        |
           +-------------------+   |   namespace:
                                   |   /dev/mouse ->
